[pycharm ubuntu 快捷方式]
sudo gedit /usr/share/applications/pycharm.desktop

'''
[Desktop Entry]
Type=Application
Name=Pycharm
GenericName=Pycharm3
Comment=Pycharm3:The Python IDE
Exec=sh /home/oliver/下载/pycharm-community-2018.1.2/bin/pycharm.sh   (sh后面是pycharm.sh的路径,直接拖拽此sh文件到终端上即可自动生成此路径,一定要写正确!!!)
Icon=/home/oliver/下载/pycharm-community-2018.1.2/bin/pycharm.png   (同理，此项也可拖拽生成路径，免去了手写的烦恼)
Terminal=pycharm
Categories=Pycharm;
'''
[pycharm ubuntu 破解]
sudo gedit /etc/hosts
0.0.0.0 account.jetbrains.com
0.0.0.0 www.jetbrains.com
1.链接: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WW1eli1DPY5eYRqmiv0cTg 提取码: kvqc
2.将补丁放在安装包的bin路径下
3.打开bin文件下的pycharm.vmoptions和pycharm64.vmoptions
4.在最后一行添加：
-javaagent:../bin/JetbrainsCrack-2.8-release-enc.jar
5.选择Activation code并输入激活码

